            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM11_DESCRIPTION3: 'YOU AGREE TO DEFEND, INDEMNIFY, AND HOLD HARMLESS THE YIPTV PARTIES FROM AND AGAINST ANY AND ALL LIABILITIES, CLAIMS, DAMAGES, EXPENSES (INCLUDING REASONABLE ATTORNEYS&#39; FEES AND COSTS), AND OTHER LOSSES ARISING OUT OF OR IN ANY WAY RELATED TO YOUR BREACH OR ALLEGED BREACH OF THESE TERMS OR YOUR USE OF THE YIPTV SERVICES (INCLUDING YOUR USE OF THE CONTENT). YIPTV RESERVES THE RIGHT, AT OUR OWN EXPENSE, TO EMPLOY SEPARATE COUNSEL AND ASSUME THE EXCLUSIVE DEFENSE AND CONTROL OF ANY MATTER OTHERWISE SUBJECT TO INDEMNIFICATION BY YOU.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM12_TITLE: '12.  NOTICE AND PROCEDURE FOR CLAIMS OF COPYRIGHT INFRINGEMENT',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM12_DESCRIPTION1: 'If you believe that any Content, User Material, or other material provided through the YipTV Services, including through a link, infringes your copyright, you should notify YipTV of your infringement claim in accordance with the procedure set forth below.',
