            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM12_DESCRIPTION4: 'To be effective, the notification must be in writing and contain the following information: (i) an electronic or physical signature of the person authorized to act on behalf of the owner of an exclusive copyright interest; (ii) a description of the copyrighted work that you claim has been infringed; (iii) a description of where the material that you claim is infringing is located on the YipTV Services that is reasonably sufficient to enable YipTV to identify and locate the material; (iv) how YipTV can contact you, such as your address, telephone number, and email address; (v) a statement by you that you have a good faith belief that the disputed use is not authorized by the copyright owner, its agent, or the law; and (vi) a statement by you that the above information in your notice is accurate and under penalty of perjury that you are authorized to act on behalf of the copyright owner or the owner of an exclusive right in the material. Emails sent to dmca@yiptv.com for purposes other than communication about copyright infringement may not be answered.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM12_DESCRIPTION5: 'YipTV has a policy of terminating repeat infringers in appropriate circumstances.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_TITLE: '13.  ARBITRATION OF CLAIMS',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_WARNING: 'PLEASE READ THIS CAREFULLY. WE WANT YOU TO KNOW IT AFFECTS YOUR RIGHTS.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION1: 'At YipTV, we expect that our world-class customer service team will be able to resolve most issues you may have using the YipTV Services. In the unlikely event that we do not meet your satisfaction, we prefer to specify now what each of us should expect in order to avoid any confusion later. Accordingly, you and YipTV agree to the following resolution process.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION2: 'To begin with, you agree that that any claim that you might have against us regarding these Terms of Use, the YipTV Services, or the Properties must be resolved through binding arbitration before the American Arbitration Association using its Commercial Arbitration Rules. It&#39;s important to us that we address any issues you might have promptly. To help us do that, you agree to begin any arbitration within one year after your claim arose; otherwise, your claim is waived. As an exception to this arbitration agreement, YipTV is happy to give you the right to pursue in small claims court any claim that is within that court&#39;s jurisdiction as long as you proceed only on an individual basis.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION3: 'Because we prefer to resolve our issues with you directly, you agree to arbitrate with YipTV only in your individual capacity, not as a representative or member of a class. As such, your claims may not be joined with any other claims and there shall be no authority for any dispute to be arbitrated on a class-action basis or brought by a purported class representative.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION4: 'Rather than force everyone to visit us in Florida, if you can demonstrate that arbitration in Florida would create an undue burden to you, you are free to initiate the arbitration in your home state. Otherwise, the arbitration hearings will be held in West Palm Beach, Florida.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION5: 'It is important that you understand that the arbitrator&#39;s decision will be binding and may be entered as a judgment in any court of competent jurisdiction. If the arbitrator rules against YipTV, in addition to accepting whatever responsibility is ordered by the arbitrator, we think it&#39;s fair that YipTV reimburse your reasonable attorneys&#39; fees and costs.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION6: 'If you&#39;re not sure what all of this means, of course please feel free to ask an attorney.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION7: 'Since we always prefer to find ways to satisfy you as quickly and efficiently as possible, before initiating any arbitration proceeding, you agree to first discuss the matter informally with YipTV for at least 30 days. To do that, please send your full name and contact information, your concern and your proposed solution by mail to us at: YipTV, Inc., 222 Lakeview Ave, Ste 160-186, West Palm Beach, FL 33401 - Attn: Legal Department.',
            TERMS_OF_USE_TERM13_DESCRIPTION8: 'Specifying what happens if an issue arises with one of our users is never a fun topic. But we pride ourselves on transparency and we thank you in advance for understanding why it’s important that you and YipTV agree on the process described in this Section.',
